<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.262987>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Dorsal (A), lateral (B) and ventral (C) views of the head of Amphisbaena filiformis sp. nov. holotype (MPEG 27916)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/262987/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.262988>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Dorsal view of midbody annulus of Amphisbaena filiformis sp. nov. (MPEG 27918). The arrow points to the lateral (1 and 3) and dorsal (2) sulci." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/262988/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.262989>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Ventral view of cloacal region of Amphisbaena filiformis sp. nov. (MPEG 27919). The arrow points to the autotomic annulus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/262989/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.262990>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Oblique view of the tail of Amphisbaena filiformis sp. nov. (MPEG 27919). Note the vertical keel of the extreme tip." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/262990/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.262991>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Amphisbaena filiformis sp. nov. in life (not identified specimen of type series) from Babaçulândia municipality, State of Tocantins, Brazil. Photo by C. E. D. Cintra." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/262991/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.262986>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Geographic distribution of Amphisbaena filiformis sp. nov. from Brazilian Cerrado. Red star represents distribution of paratypes in the right bank of Tocantins River, Estreito municipality, State of Maranhão. Red star with a black central dot represents type-locality in the left bank of Tocantins River, Babaçulândia municipality, State of Tocantins; Brazil." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/262986/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.262992>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. “ Floresta Ombrófila Aberta das Terras Baixas ” with palm tree forest in center, municipality of Babaçulândia, State of Tocantins, where the holotype of Amphisbaena filiformis sp. nov. was collected." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/262992/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

